-- Ahmadinejad Invites Assad to Non-Aligned Summit, IRNA Says
-- B y   L a d a n e   N a s s e r i
-- 2012-05-24T13:13:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-24/ahmadinejad-invites-assad-to-non-aligned-summit-irna-says.html
Iranian President  Mahmoud Ahmadinejad 
has invited his Syrian counterpart, Bashar al-Assad, to visit
Tehran to take part in a meeting of the  Non-Aligned Movement ,
the official  Islamic Republic News Agency  reported.  The summit is scheduled for the last week of August in the
Iranian capital, according to the report.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ladane Nasseri in Dubai at 
 lnasseri@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew J. Barden at 
 barden@bloomberg.net  